additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Intentionally misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. For advice, contact a Poison Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26, New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If in eyes, wash out with plenty of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor.
